      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "按最短作业优先原则，P1的CPU burst是5个时间单位，P2是3，P3是4，P4最短只有2。时间轴用纯数字格式X，显示为秒数百分比格式。标题定为\"Planificación SJF Non-Preemptive - Parte 1 (IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream)\"。",
